data.description: ****New Home, Ready for Immediate Move-In, Builder Warranty updated. Ask about Closing Cost credits!**** Welcome to your dream home in the serene Raven Oaks subdivision! As you step inside, you'll immediately notice the Luxury Vinyl Plank flooring, a grand island with seating, Home theater speaker grills installed in the great groom ceiling; Ready to use/ New Appliances - Gas Stove with multi-option Oven, including an Air Fryer mode, Washer and Dryer, Refrigerator, Gas Fireplace, Window Blinds in each window, Microwave with ventilation.  Built in 2022 with SMARTCOM security, cable, internet prewiring, sensors at each door, control panels upper and lower levels, this stunning 4 bedroom, 3 bathroom masterpiece is the epitome of modern living and offers a truly unparalleled experience. This brand new home boasts exquisite design, luxurious amenities, and a prime location with the attention to detail and craftsmanship. The main level features a convenient bedroom with a full bathroom, making it perfect for guests or multi-generational living. This thoughtful layout provides flexibility and convenience for all your needs. The heart of the home is the open-concept living area, where natural light pours in through large windows, creating a bright and inviting space. The gourmet kitchen is a chef's delight, with gleaming quartz countertops that provide ample workspace for culinary endeavors and with an eat-in area and a spacious island with seating it is an ideal spot for family gatherings and entertaining guests. Step outside onto the expansive deck that overlooks your private lot, backing to a tranquil wooded area - It is an outdoor oasis with the perfect backdrop for all your outdoor activities. Upstairs, you'll find a convenient laundry area and a versatile loft with viewable distant mountain peaks; the space can be transformed to suit your needs – a home office, playroom, or a cozy reading nook. 3 additional well-appointed bedrooms offer plenty of space for family and guests. This home is the "Pearl" model, known for its elegance and modern design. It's a testament to quality and style, providing a comfortable and sophisticated living environment. The Raven Oaks subdivision is not just a place to live; it's a lifestyle. Situated conveniently close to commuter routes, shopping centers, and various amenities, popular restaurants you'll have everything you need within easy reach. From the moment you step inside, you'll be captivated by the beauty and functionality of this home. Don't miss the opportunity to make this magnificent property your own. Schedule a viewing today and experience the perfect blend of luxury, convenience, and natural beauty in this exceptional 4 bedroom, 3 bathroom home. Your dream home awaits! Beautiful large, private Lot, one if a kind! MUST SEE!
